  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940980/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764935346\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940980/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764935346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1940980/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764935346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Fortress Building Puzzle is a puzzle game where you need to remove all the cubes to bring your castle to the ground, which is quite high.<br><br>You can choose the degree of difficulty from 1 to 7 floors of cubes.<br><br>Game Features: <br>- Unlimited time to bring the castle to the ground, so at difficult levels you can stay for hours<br>- All levels have a solution, and everything here is based on physics<br>- Choose the degree of dificulty you want<br>- Direct your view to the tower with the help of arrows from the keyboard or those from the screen",
  "about_the_game": "Fortress Building Puzzle is a puzzle game where you need to remove all the cubes to bring your castle to the ground, which is quite high.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can choose the degree of difficulty from 1 to 7 floors of cubes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features: <br />\r\n- Unlimited time to bring the castle to the ground, so at difficult levels you can stay for hours<br />\r\n- All levels have a solution, and everything here is based on physics<br />\r\n- Choose the degree of dificulty you want<br />\r\n- Direct your view to the tower with the help of arrows from the keyboard or those from the screen",
